 Community involvement
We understand that wealth refers to more than just one's finances. It also includes a sense of prosperity and well-being in the communities in which we live and work. Through our dedication to arts, youth, sport and sustainability, RBC Wealth Management is able to inspire a path to success for emerging artists, amateur and professional athletes, and young leaders dedicated to a better future.














Fundraiser
Guernsey Harbour Carnival

                                                                                                                                                             St Peter Port, Guernsey
                    
RBC Wealth Management celebrates 10 years of support of the Guernsey Harbour Carnival, an annual fun-filled community event in and around St Peter Port Harbour.
Learn more















Fundraiser
RBC Race for the Kids
RBC Race for the Kids is a global race series that brings families, communities and RBC employees together to raise money for local children’s charities.
Learn more















Arts and culture
BFI London Film Festival

                                                                                                                                                             London, UK
                    
Royal Bank of Canada celebrates 61 years of film excellence by partnering with the British Film Institute to sponsor the London Film Festival from October 4-15, 2017.
Learn more
























