Worldwide locations













The international division of RBC Wealth Management has a global network of offices in major financial centres around the world. 
No matter which office serves as your primary point of contact, specialists in other offices are always available to provide you with additional expertise and service. Through a single relationship manager, you will have access to a complete range of sophisticated wealth management and private banking services*.



Asia









China







This Representative office of RBC Wealth Management provides access to RBC's worldwide network of offices.



Suite 925A, Winland Centre, No. 7,
                        Finance Street, Xi Cheng District
                        Beijing 100033 P.R. China




Tel. + 86-10-5839-9300 
Fax + 86-10-5839-9363



* Depending on your citizenship and/or residence, some products and services may not be available to you or may only be available to you from certain RBC Wealth Management offices.

 









Hong Kong







Our Hong Kong office is home to a large team of dedicated professionals who provide valuable local knowledge, the advantage of a truly international team of specialists, and access to a complete range of wealth management services through our global network of offices*.



17/F Cheung Kong Center
                        2 Queen's Road Central Hong Kong




Tel. + 852-2848-1388 
Fax + 852-2521-2968



* Depending on your citizenship and/or residence, some products and services may not be available to you or may only be available to you from certain RBC Wealth Management offices.

 









